  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were in power for quite a while, and they were not as, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would say brutal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what use-- what they used.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is one of the reasons that some of the Austrian, old Nazis, who had gone through the times that the Nationalist Socialist Democratic Party was prohibited in Austria-- underground, fifth column-- were terribly disappointed after the Anschluss, because they expected to be rewarded.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in came the German Nazis and took the top positions, and the Austrians were still the underlings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I could tell you something about that-- I mentioned that we lived in a villa where the land-- the owner, lived on the first floor-- first floor in Vienna meant one flight up.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] owner had bought that villa from the estate of-- of some defunct noble family-- you know, they needed the money, whatever-- and-- and gutted it and modernized it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was a friend of my father's-- friend, sort of an acquaintance of my father's.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, why don't you take the upstairs, and you'll give me an amount for building expenses, and I can arrange this upstairs to your liking and to your needs.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so my father and the architect drew the lines where this room would be and that room and where the bathroom and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, certain things were a given, but others could be switched around and the modern bathrooms put in an so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is how come we lived up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But this gentlemen was married to a Gentile [INAUDIBLE] lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
